## Inline Annotations

Tag type and description in source comments. `FIXME`, `BUG`, and `HACK` are merge-blocked by CI.

| Tag | Use |
|-----|-----|
| `TODO` | Planned work |
| `FIXME` | Broken behavior |
| `HACK` | Fragile workaround |
| `BUG` | Active defect |
| `NOTE` | Informational, no action |

Format: uppercase tag, colon, imperative description. Include an issue reference when possible.
```
// TODO: implement retry logic (#42)
// FIXME: panics on empty input
```

Never merge `FIXME`, `BUG`, or `HACK` into `main`. Convert to a tracked issue or resolve before merging.
